<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="374" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,1653,2019]" pageId="1" pageNumber="374">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1922,1947]" pageId="1" pageNumber="374">Remarks.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[379,427,1923,1947]" pageId="1" pageNumber="374">type</typeStatus>
species is well separated from other species of the genus by an absence of wide dark pattern on forewings.
</paragraph>
